<h2 class="bold font-l">Shufflegate</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After Mario and Huey prove the Toad was cheating in his shuffling event, the Toad says the event could be called Shufflegate. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Gate Construction</span>, <span>Gate Suffix</span> </h3>
